				</a>
				<a
					href="/aec/revit-specialists/"
					class="js-fade-in group rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20 transition hover:border-aec/30 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-300"
				>
					<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-aec">Revit Specialists</p>
					<h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">Revit Specialists</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Dedicated Revit experts across MEP, Structure, and Architecture disciplines.</p>
