						Choose Your Engagement Model
					</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
						Start with a single specialist or scale a full production pod. Month-to-month, no long-term contracts.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<a
						href="/aec/individuals/"
						class="js-fade-in group rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-black/20 transition hover:border-aec/30 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-300"
					>
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-aec">Individual Specialists</p>
